{"article_id":"bBqEKJ6ZVdBQTAO1","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Snowden had been at the Moscow airport for more than a month .","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"Snowden gets Russian asylum","depth":2},{"id":2,"text":"NSA leaker Edward Snowden has left the Moscow airport ,","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"entered Russia","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"and been granted one-year temporary asylum ,","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"according to reports Thursday .","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"\" Over the past eight weeks we have seen the Obama administration show no respect for international or domestic law ,","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"but in the end the law is winning .","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"I thank the Russian Federation","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"for granting me asylum in accordance with its laws and international obligations , \"","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"Snowden said","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"upon receiving his certificate ,","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"according to WikiLeaks .","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"WikiLeaks released a statement about his departure ,","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"saying","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"the one-year asylum will allow Snowden to live and travel freely within Russia","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"as he plans his next steps .","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"Snowden ,","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"who has been living in the transit area of the Moscow airport for 39 days ,","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"had been waiting on necessary paperwork","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"to leave ,","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"which arrived Thursday .","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"\" I have just handed over to him papers from the Russian Immigration Service .","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"They are what he needs","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"to leave the transit zone , \"","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"Snowden ' s Russian legal representative Anatoly Kucherena told Interfax ,","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"according to RT.com ,","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"which also reported","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"that he has been granted a one-year temporary asylum .","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"The Russian news site also reported","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"that Snowden left the airport about 30 minutes before his refugee status was announced for an undisclosed location ,","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"which will remain secret .","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"He left with WikiLeaks ' s Sarah Harrison ,","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"WikiLeak said ,","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"who has been with him during the entirety of his stay in Russia and during his exit from Hong Kong .","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"\" Ms Harrison has remained with Mr. Snowden at all times","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"to protect his safety and security , \"","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"WikiLeaks said .","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"As news of Snowden ' s release spread Thursday morning ,","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"lawmakers expressed their displeasure with Russia ' s decision","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"to grant Snowden temporary asylum .","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"The chairman of the Senate Foreign Relations Committee said","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"Russia ' s move did damage to the country ' s relationship with the United States","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"and called for Russia to send Snowden home","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"to face trial .","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"\" Edward Snowden is a fugitive","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"who belongs in a United States courtroom ,","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"not a free man","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"deserving of asylum in Russia , \"","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"Sen. Robert Menendez","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"( D-N.J. )","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"said in a statement .","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"\" Regardless of the fact","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"that Russia is granting asylum for one year ,","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"this action is a setback to U.S.-Russia relations .","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"Edward Snowden will potentially do great damage to U.S. national security interests","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"and the information","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"he is leaking","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"could aid terrorists and others around the world","depth":12},{"id":59,"text":"who want to do real harm to our country . \"","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"Sen. Tom Coburn","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"( R-Okla. )","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"also said","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"the development damages the U.S.-Russia relationship","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"and Snowden ' s stay in the country threatens U.S. security .","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"\" I think","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"it probably hurts the relationship ,","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"you know","depth":14},{"id":68,"text":"he ' s undoubtedly in my mind a traitor to our country","depth":14},{"id":69,"text":"and probably most of what he knows , the Russians already know . ...","depth":13},{"id":70,"text":"It ' s a gold mine for them , \"","depth":12},{"id":71,"text":"Coburn said Thursday morning on MSNBC ' s \" Morning Joe . \"","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"Snowden had been staying at the Moscow airport for more than a month","depth":6},{"id":73,"text":"since leaving Hong Kong ,","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"where he initially fled to from the U.S. , for Russia in late June .","depth":7},{"id":75,"text":"White House press secretary Jay Carney said","depth":5},{"id":76,"text":"the administration was \" extremely disappointed \" with the move on Thursday .","depth":5},{"id":77,"text":"The administration had repeatedly said","depth":6},{"id":78,"text":"Russia should extradite Snowden back to the U.S .","depth":6},{"id":79,"text":"Just last week , the United States had continued its pressure on the Russian government to release Snowden ,","depth":6},{"id":80,"text":"with Attorney General Eric Holder sending his Russian counterpart a letter","depth":7},{"id":81,"text":"assuring","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"that Snowden would not face the death penalty in the U.S .","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"Snowden reportedly agreed to stop harming the U.S.","depth":6},{"id":84,"text":"by leaking information as a condition of asylum last month .","depth":6},{"id":85,"text":"However , The Guardian has continued to publish information","depth":7},{"id":86,"text":"initially provided to them by Snowden ,","depth":7},{"id":87,"text":"including a report on Wednesday","depth":7},{"id":88,"text":"that the NSA has a tool","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"to monitor Internet activity .","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":179,"left":91,"right":178,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":91,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":178,"left":126,"right":177,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":126,"left":105,"right":125,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":105,"left":94,"right":104,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":94,"left":93,"right":5,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":93,"left":2,"right":92,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":92,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":104,"left":100,"right":103,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":100,"left":99,"right":12,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":99,"left":95,"right":98,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":95,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":98,"left":96,"right":97,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":96,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":97,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":103,"left":13,"right":102,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":102,"left":14,"right":101,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":101,"left":15,"right":16,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":125,"left":116,"right":12